overview.en: The Star Wonderful Stars project aim to Star project and serves beautiful business. It is committed to building a brand new pan entertainment content ecosystem (including short video, live broadcast, game, etc.) by using block chain technology. Through the distributed architecture, a pan entertainment open community ecosystem is established to create an internationalized incentive pan entertainment platform.
overview.zh: 星美星SWS项目锁定明星项目、服务美丽事业，致力于利用区块链技术塑造全新的泛娱乐内容生态圈（包括短视频、直播、游戏、网剧等内容），通过分布式架构，建立泛娱乐开放式社区生态系统，打造国际化的激励型泛娱乐生态平台。
